.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REBALANCE-HISTORY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-rebalance-history \- list past rebalance payments
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-rebalance-history
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns payments whose description contains "rebalance".
Default limit is 20.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{payment_hash, status, amount_msat, created_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-rebalance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-rebalance-check (1)
